    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Sirocellus iunctus gen. et sp. nov., male holotype (GPIH05128). A. Whole specimen, dorsolateral view. B. Same, ventrolateral view. C. Camera lucida drawing of A. D. Same of B. Abbreviations: ad, adenostyle; ch, chelicerae; fe, femur; mt, metatarsus; oz, ozophore; pa, patella; pp, pedipalp; ta, tarsus; ti, tibia; tr, trochanter; legs numbered from I–IV. Scale bars equal 1 mm (A, C, D) and 0.5 mm (B)." ;
